Package com.espertech.esper.epl.expression

This package contains the EPL expression nodes that represent all expressions such as used in select clauses, group-by and having clauses, or order-by clauses

This package contains the EPL expression nodes that represent all expressions such as used in select clauses, group-by and having clauses, or order-by clauses
